WEBVTT

00:00:02.787 --> 00:00:04.621
Zakaj se svet segreva?

00:00:06.829 --> 00:00:08.496
Za trenutek si zamislimo Zemljo

00:00:08.496 --> 00:00:09.871
kot toplo gredo.

00:00:10.913 --> 00:00:13.329
Vsako sekundo ogromna količina energije

00:00:13.329 --> 00:00:15.329
trči v našo toplo gredo.

00:00:16.913 --> 00:00:20.163
Naša atmosfera, steklena streha in stene,

00:00:20.163 --> 00:00:22.496
odbija nekaj energije,

00:00:22.538 --> 00:00:26.079
a večina prodre skozi in vse se segreva.

00:00:27.329 --> 00:00:29.871
Veliko toplote 
se je prej vračalo v vesolje

00:00:29.871 --> 00:00:32.621
in ohranjala se je stabilna,
topla temperatura.